---
description: Add a REST endpoint to an existing controller + register the route (modify-aware generator).
argument-hint: <Resource> <METHOD> <path>
---
Run `gofasta g endpoint $ARGUMENTS --dry-run --json` first to
preview the planned edits (e.g.
`gofasta g endpoint Order POST /orders/{id}/archive`). Surface the
controller/service/route changes, then re-run without `--dry-run`
to apply if approved. Run `gofasta swagger` after to refresh
OpenAPI docs.
